HTML_EDITING_INSTRUCTION_TEXT: Author a learning activity by entering HTML in the editor below. Do not include <html>, <head>, or <body> tags. The system will automatically include those tags. To include images, add them to the "Resources" section below. After uploading images, you will need to click the "Copy Embed Code" button to copy and paste the embed code into the HTML editor. To include CSS and JavaScript files, include a Web Package Dependency. Within the web package, include CSS and JavaScript files in dependency order. For example, if a JavaScript file requires JQuery then include the JQuery library file first. You can reorder web package files using the up and down arrows.
